title: By the Supreame Councell of the Confederate Catholiques of Ireland wee the Supreame Councell of the said Confederate Catholiques, hauing of a long tyme, with deepe sense of the sufferings of the people and the wayes taken to heape miseries on this afflicted kingdome ...
author: Confederate Catholics. Supreme Council.
publicationDate: In the Yeare of our Lord, 1648.
